                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 81vb: This book is of ʾabunä Rǝʾǝsä Haymanot who donated it to ʾAraʿro Qǝddus Mikaʾel. May His prayer and blessing be with his servant ʾabunä qäsis Rǝʾǝsä Haymanot. Do not forget me in your prayers. For ever and ever Amen. And his wife Wälättä Giyorgis.</q>
                           The text is written over an erasure in red ink. The name of the wife Wälättä Giyorgis may have been added later.
